These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Movie-Genre: martial-arts, drama, animation, action
Flower: rose, tulip, daisy, aconite
1. Flower:tulip is on the left of Flower:rose##1
2. Movie-Genre:martial-arts == Flower:aconite##1
3. Flower:daisy is on the right of Flower:rose##1
4. Movie-Genre:drama is on the left of Flower:aconite##1
5. Movie-Genre:action is on the left of Flower:rose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | action | animation | drama | martial-arts   |
| Flower   | tulip  | rose     | daisy   | aconite |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Transport: scooter, airplane, quad-bike, boat
Flower: daffodil, tulip, amaryllis, aconite
1. Transport:boat == Flower:tulip##1
2. Transport:scooter is on the far right##1
3. Transport:airplane is on the right of Transport:boat##1
4. Transport:boat is on the right of Flower:amaryllis##1
5. Flower:tulip is on the left of Flower:daffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Transport   | quad-bike | boat | airplane | scooter    |
| Flower   | amaryllis    | tulip      | daffodil | aconite |

