.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
Sport: skateboarding, golf, sailing, badminton
Game: scrabble, backgammon, whist, poker
1. Game:scrabble is on the left of Sport:golf##1
2. Game:backgammon is on the left of Sport:badminton##1
3. Sport:skateboarding is on the left of Sport:sailing##1
4. Sport:badminton == Game:poker##1
5. Game:scrabble is on the left of Sport:golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport   | skateboarding | sailing | golf | badminton   |
| Game     | whist  | scrabble    | backgammon       | poker |

 